<h1>Problem 11 - 2017 IMO, P2 of 6</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 9</h2>
<p>Let \(\mathbb{R}\) be the set of real numbers. Determine all functions \(f : \mathbb{R} \to \mathbb{R}\) such that, for all real numbers \(x\) and \(y\), \[f(f(x)f(y)) + f(x + y) = f(xy).\]</p>
